<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM5.4">
<l>vāḷā laṟuttuc cuṭiṉum maruttuvaṉpāl</l>
<l>māḷāta kātalnō yāḷaṉpōl māyattāl</l>
<l>mīḷāt tuyartariṉum viṟṟuvakkōṭ ṭammāṉī</l>
<l>āḷā vuṉataruḷē pārppa ṉaṭiyēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like the sick man who [bears] undying affection for the physician</l>
<l>even though [he] cuts [him] with a knife [and] sears, O Lord of Viṟṟuvakkōṭu!</l>
<l>Even though through maya You give [me] suffering that does not disappear</l>
<l>I, who am [your] servant, shall look for the grace of You, who have not accepted [me].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
